        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># title【必需】文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line">title: 文章创建模板</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># date【必需】文章创建日期</span></span><br><span class="line">date: 2023-05-07 15:57:14</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># updated【可选】文章更新日期</span></span><br><span class="line">updated: </span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># tags【可选】文章标签</span></span><br><span class="line">tags: # 标签可根据内容随意写</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> hexo</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> 文章</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># categories【可选】文章分类</span></span><br><span class="line">categories: 计算机 # 大学生涯 / 生活日常 / 闲杂琐碎 / 个人总结 /奇闻趣事 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># top<span class="emphasis">_img【可选】文章顶部图片</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section"># top_</span>img: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># 【可选】文章缩略图(如果没有设置 top<span class="emphasis">_img,文章页顶部将显示缩略图，可设为 false/图片地址/留空)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section">cover: https://qny.hanxi.fun/img/a13.webp</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section"># comments【可选】显示文章评论模块(默认 true)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section">comments: true</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section"># swiper_</span>index【可选】首页轮播图配置 index 索引，数字越小越靠前</span></span><br><span class="line">swiper<span class="emphasis">_index: 1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># top_</span>group<span class="emphasis">_index【可选】首页右侧卡片组配置, 数字越小越靠前</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">top_</span>group<span class="emphasis">_index: 1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># background【可选】文章背景可配置为 16 进制颜色值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">background: &quot;#FF43ED&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># 【推荐】hexo-generator-index 从 2.0.0 开始，已经支持文章置顶功能。你可以直接在文章的 front-matter 区域里添加 sticky: 1 属性来把这篇文章置顶。数值越大，置顶的优先级越大。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">sticky: 2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># 如果有文章（例如：转载文章）不需要显示版权，可以在文章 Front-matter 单独设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># copyright: false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># 支持对单独文章设置版权信息，可以在文章 Front-matter 单独设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># 文章作者</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"># copyright_</span>author: xxxx</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># 作者链接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># copyright<span class="emphasis">_author_</span>href: https://xxxxxx.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># 文章链接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># copyright<span class="emphasis">_url: https://xxxxxx.com</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section"># 版权声明</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="section"># copyright_</span>info: 此文章版权归xxxxx所有，如有转载，请注明来自原作者</span></span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
