      <title>Ubuntu22.04安装docker</title>
      <link href="/2023/04/25/Ubuntu22.04%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85docker/"/>
      <url>/2023/04/25/Ubuntu22.04%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85docker/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="设置存储库"><a href="#设置存储库" class="headerlink" title="设置存储库"></a>设置存储库</h3><h4 id="1-更新软件包索引并安装软件包以允许使用-基于-HTTPS-的存储库：apt-apt"><a href="#1-更新软件包索引并安装软件包以允许使用-基于-HTTPS-的存储库：apt-apt" class="headerlink" title="1.更新软件包索引并安装软件包以允许使用 基于 HTTPS 的存储库：apt``apt"></a>1.更新软件包索引并安装软件包以允许使用 基于 HTTPS 的存储库：<code>apt``apt</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install \</span><br><span class="line">    ca-certificates \</span><br><span class="line">    curl \</span><br><span class="line">    gnupg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-添加-Docker-的官方-GPG-密钥："><a href="#2-添加-Docker-的官方-GPG-密钥：" class="headerlink" title="2.添加 Docker 的官方 GPG 密钥："></a>2.添加 Docker 的官方 GPG 密钥：</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -m 0755 -p /etc/apt/keyrings</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-使用以下命令设置存储库："><a href="#3-使用以下命令设置存储库：" class="headerlink" title="3.使用以下命令设置存储库："></a>3.使用以下命令设置存储库：</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">echo \</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;deb [arch=&quot;$(dpkg --print-architecture)&quot; signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu \</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;$(. /etc/os-release &amp;&amp; echo &quot;$VERSION_CODENAME&quot;)&quot; stable&quot; | \</span><br><span class="line">  sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list &gt; /dev/null</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装-Docker-引擎"><a href="#安装-Docker-引擎" class="headerlink" title="安装 Docker 引擎"></a>安装 Docker 引擎</h3><h4 id="1-更新包索引：apt"><a href="#1-更新包索引：apt" class="headerlink" title="1.更新包索引：apt"></a>1.更新包索引：<code>apt</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>尝试授予 Docker 的读取权限 更新包索引之前的公钥文件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-安装-Docker-Engine、containerd-和-Docker-Compose。"><a href="#2-安装-Docker-Engine、containerd-和-Docker-Compose。" class="headerlink" title="2.安装 Docker Engine、containerd 和 Docker Compose。"></a>2.安装 Docker Engine、containerd 和 Docker Compose。</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin docker-compose-plugin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-通过运行映像验证-Docker-引擎安装是否成功：hello-world"><a href="#3-通过运行映像验证-Docker-引擎安装是否成功：hello-world" class="headerlink" title="3.通过运行映像验证 Docker 引擎安装是否成功：hello-world"></a>3.通过运行映像验证 Docker 引擎安装是否成功：<code>hello-world</code></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo docker run hello-world</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="4-防止Docker自动更新"><a href="#4-防止Docker自动更新" class="headerlink" title="4.防止Docker自动更新"></a>4.防止Docker自动更新</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-mark hold docker-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="5-允许非root用户使用Docker"><a href="#5-允许非root用户使用Docker" class="headerlink" title="5.允许非root用户使用Docker"></a>5.允许非root用户使用Docker</h4><p>默认情况下只有root权限才可以使用Docker，使用下列命令将用户加入到Docker组。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo usermod -aG docker $USER</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="6-查看安装的版本"><a href="#6-查看安装的版本" class="headerlink" title="6.查看安装的版本"></a>6.查看安装的版本</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker compose version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="7-配置镜像加速"><a href="#7-配置镜像加速" class="headerlink" title="7.配置镜像加速"></a>7.配置镜像加速</h4><p>您可以通过修改daemon配置文件/etc/docker/daemon.json来使用加速器</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mkdir -p /etc/docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo tee /etc/docker/daemon.json &lt;&lt;-&#x27;EOF&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;registry-mirrors&quot;: [&quot;https://elz0vctf.mirror.aliyuncs.com&quot;]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">EOF</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl restart docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="8-Docker-Compose-安装"><a href="#8-Docker-Compose-安装" class="headerlink" title="8.Docker Compose 安装"></a>8.Docker Compose 安装</h4><p>root模式下执行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.25.5/docker-compose-`uname -s`-`uname -m` &gt; /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="9-卸载-Docker"><a href="#9-卸载-Docker" class="headerlink" title="9.卸载 Docker"></a>9.卸载 Docker</h4><p>卸载前，先停止并删除容器、镜像，卷和网络。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker container stop $(docker container ls -aq)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker system prune -a --volumes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后删除软件、配置和软件包</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt purge docker-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt autoremove</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
